Information.ShortDescription: The Guilford offers a whole new world of features in a beautiful, old world setting. Among the century-old oaks, the quiet, sun-dappled thoroughfares and the seemingly endless rows of traditional and classic-style architecture is a place where people love to get together.
Information.LongDescription: In the midst of a magnificent neighborhood setting, we here at the Guilford have created an unparalleled collection of comforts and amenities that will take your breath away. This deco-inspired community is a fusion of classic spaciousness and urban tranquility. A vibrant social scene. Apartments with large, spacious floorplans. And endless upscale community features. Welcome to The Guilford, where you can truly have it all. Just a few short blocks from the historic campuses of Johns Hopkins and Loyola Universities, The Guilford adds every modern comfort and convenience to an area rich in tradition. It's history in the re-making. We are located on public transportation and a stop for the JHU shuttle. Check out our new student lounge.
